title: Teutonic Last Stand: Battle of the Wild Flowers - Medieval Kingdoms Total War 1212AD Mod Gameplay
description:
Teutonic Last Stand: Battle of the Wild Flowers - Medieval Kingdoms Total War 1212AD Mod Gameplay - The Teutonic Order and the Holy Roman Empire have gathered a great forced to bring down Lithuania.  But Lithuania does not stand alone, Kievan Rus sends an army to stand with the Lithuanian forces. This is a 2v2 online battle replay using the Medieval Kingdoms Total War 1212AD.  Enjoy the Battle :D

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
